Features:

User        => sign-up, sign-in, sign-out

Home page   => book search, display books

Books       => display all added books along with various user_book specific details
               allow users to create shelves
               add books to shelves

Book Details => book details
                 user activity that is related to specific book
                 add review comments
                 rate the book
                 view all reviews related to this book
                 comment against reviews

